{"tid":131671,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"一套12集嘅時空穿越動畫屌打《命運石之門》","createTime":"2017-02-23T08:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T17:26:58.000Z","uid":86488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a91bfbfbdb79f2216bd647c8e0720ed23559c984","tid":131671,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"當初我係睇完呢套動畫先睇《命運石之門》嘅<br />\n對於佢個時空穿越嘅設定已經無感<br />\n啲人仲要話11集之後好好睇<br />\n結果嚟嚟去去就係為咗救香菜<br />\n呢套12集嘅動畫只係用咗兩集鋪墊<br />\n結果係劇情、設定、人物情感都屌打SG<br />\nSG重要嘅角色係得主角同助手<br />\n其他人基本上可有可無（救香菜不過係一個目標、設定）<br />\n基本上就係叫嗰幾個人改變返自己嘅願望（仲要重複幾次）<br />\n但我講嘅嗰套嘢入面嘅每個人都有推動劇情嘅作用<br />\n一套做到20幾集嘅動畫比唔上一套季番<br />\n真係無言以對<br />\n<br />\n我講緊嗰套叫《魔法戰爭》<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">講笑，睇都冇睇過</span></span>"},{"pid":"78a73e8a80e2e65d66ef02e4163633a272ef5219","tid":131671,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e7385800db2d617136fcf93bbd803717c1b104","tid":131671,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"樓主識課<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果睇埋魔法戰爭係輕小說就知命運石之門係垃圾"},{"pid":"d5f40e0fad5dd114f1b3185d585f0b78ffb25ed1","tid":131671,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲打鬥都好好睇<br />\n尤其是學姐既魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dc8d903f20d10e99c5fa1bb61cad98a1c80a1b","tid":131671,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"點解我個隱喻咁高質都冇人黎<br />\n呢度係咪冇人識小圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977f2198e2867e6e0b1055d498188014646af7c2","tid":131671,"uid":17794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci